Grateful for this journey with pole, a practice that’s helped me embrace my body, not for how it looks, but for what it can do.
It’s taught me patience, body positivity, and the beauty of strength over aesthetics.
It’s reminded me that strong is beautiful in every shape, every size.
That expression matters more than perfection.
That flowing freely in your body is the most liberating thing.
Pole has given me more than words can hold. And i am grateful to be able to share this journey with every woman ready to embrace her power.
